{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cerebral Microgame Frenzy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play through collections of rapid-fire microgames formed from the minds of multiple colorful opponents in this cerebral story-driven take on games like WarioWare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>MAKE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP OF MINDSCAPE TOWER.\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>DELVE INTO THE MINDS OF YOUR OPPONENTS.\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>BE CONSUMED BY THE TRUTH THEY SPEAK TO YOU, IN THIS CEREBRAL BATTLE OF SIGHT AND SOUND HIDDEN WITHIN EACH OF US</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Climb the Tower</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blackout City\u2014 home to Mindscape Co., creators of the world's most played cognitive reality game: MINDWAVE. A game where players link their brains together and go head-to-head in an onslaught of feelings and memories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The time has come for Mindscape Co.'s annual MINDWAVE Tournament, hosted at Mindscape Tower. A young girl named Pandora finds herself with a Platinum Ticket, granting her entry. The only thing standing between her and the large cash prize is several rounds of nonstop mental mayhem.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Out of Your Shell</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In between rounds of the tournament, you can chat with other contestants. Get to know your opponents, analyze the competition, and maybe make a few friends.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Mind Over Matter</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Endless Mode, you can rematch the minds you've endured in Story Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survive for as long as you can while the speed, difficulty, and weirdness get cranked up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Endless Mode also features leaderboards so you can compare high scores with your buddies and enemies.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701030/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736890535","b